<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bia's World ★</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;700&family=Syne:wght@800&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg-color: #121212;
            --card-bg: #1e1e1e;
            --accent-red: #ff4d4d;
            --accent-blue: #4d94ff;
            --text-color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-family: 'Space+Grotesk', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border: 3px dashed var(--accent-red);
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1a1a1a, #252525);
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            color: white;
        }

        .nickname {
            color: var(--accent-blue);
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .section {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-blue);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .section:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            border-left-color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 0;
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: lowercase;
        }

        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #333;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin: 5px;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .color-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .swatch {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid white;
        }

        .red { background-color: var(--accent-red); }
        .blue { background-color: var(--accent-blue); }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .star {
            color: var(--accent-red);
        }

        /* Fun decorative elements */
        .decor {
            position: fixed;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.1;
            font-size: 5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>BEATRIZ SENA</h1>
            <p class="nickname">Bia ★ Luua</p>
            <p>13 years old • Aries • MG → SP</p>
        </header>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>I was born in Minas Gerais and lived there until I was 4. Now I live in São Paulo! I have brown hair with blonde highlights and big brown eyes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>My Art Journey</h2>
            <p>I've loved art since I was little. I'm always trying new things:</p>
            <span class="tag">Drawing</span>
            <span class="tag">Piano</span>
            <span class="tag">Origami</span>
            <span class="tag">Flute</span>
            <span class="tag">Acoustic Guitar</span>
            <p><strong>Current Mission:</strong> Learning the electric guitar! 🎸</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>My Favorites</h2>
            <p>I love red because it matches me, and blue because it's special to me and my friend.</p>
            <div class="color-box">
                <div class="swatch red"></div>
                <div class="swatch blue"></div>
            </div>
            <p>I also love <strong>plushies</strong> and creating my own characters!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Watch List</h2>
            <p><strong>Cartoons:</strong> Adventure Time, The Owl House, Gravity Falls, Fionna and Cake, Kid Cosmic.</p>
            <p><strong>Anime:</strong> Blue Period, The Summer Hikaru Died, Little Witch Academia.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>My Support System</h2>
            <p>My family and friends (real and virtual) are everything to me. And my cats are the best—they make me laugh after a long day! 🐾</p>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>Made with <span class="star">★</span> by Bia</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
